hifiberry-webui (0.2.5) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added nginx API proxy configuration (hifiberry-api.nginx)
  * API requests to /api are now proxied to localhost:1080/api
  * Updated configure-webui script to include both web UI and API configurations
  * Added WebSocket support for real-time API features
  * Simplified build process to always build fresh Vue.js files

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 03 Jul 2025 16:30:00 +0000

hifiberry-webui (0.2.4) stable; urgency=medium

  * Updated API configuration for production deployment
  * API now runs on same server at /api path instead of separate port
  * Added automatic API URL rewriting during package build
  * Improved integration with nginx reverse proxy setup

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 03 Jul 2025 16:00:00 +0000

