hifiberry-webui (0.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Improved build system
  * Bug fixes and improvements in UI
  * Switched from audiocontrol integration to dedicated nginx service
  * Added proper SPA routing support with nginx
  * Re-enabled cache-busting hashes for optimal caching
  * Changed from port 8080 to standard HTTP port 80
  * Added comprehensive configure-webui management script
  
